data.description: Welcome to your dream home in beautiful Colorado Springs! This stunning tri-level home offers the perfect blend of modern comfort, natural beauty, and convenient location. With three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a host of impressive features, this property is a true gem.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting interior. The main level features an open-concept living and dining area, complete with large windows that frame breathtaking mountain views. The centerpiece of the living room is a cozy fireplace, perfect for those chilly Colorado evenings. The updated bathrooms are a true highlight, offering modern fixtures and finishes.    The kitchen boasts ample cabinet space, and stainless steel appliances. It flows seamlessly into a second living room space, providing versatility for entertaining or relaxing. The two additional bedrooms on the upper level are spacious and offer plenty of natural light.    The exterior of this home is equally impressive. Enjoy your morning coffee on the patio as you take in panoramic mountain views. The backyard backs up to open space, ensuring privacy and a serene atmosphere. The new roof adds to the property's value and ensures peace of mind for years to come.     This home's location is a standout feature. It is conveniently situated near three military bases: Fort Carson, Peterson Air Force Base, and Schriever Air Force Base. Downtown Colorado Springs is just a short drive away, offering a vibrant urban experience with dining, shopping, and cultural attractions. Plus, you'll be only 5 minutes from the Colorado Springs Airport, making travel a breeze.    This home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and natural beauty. With updated features, mountain views, and a prime location, it's the perfect place to call home in Colorado Springs. Don't miss your chance to make this remarkable property yours!
